snippet.title: Team Assault the Canceled Mass Effect 3 FPS
snippet.description: "Team Assaul"t the Canceled Mass Effect 3 FPS. Bioware worked on Team Assault shortly after the Mass Effect 2 was finished. Take a look at this short gameplay trailer of this short-lived Mass Effect FPS, Mass Effect: Team Assault. Do You think Bioware should give a chance to a FPS version of Mass Effect ?
